{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setuser:emails:completion:"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:v"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"text":"setUser:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"userId","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"emails:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSArray","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSArray"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"emails"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"completion:","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"(","kind":"text"},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" (^"},{"text":")(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The custom user identifier."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"userId"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Array of email address strings.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"emails"},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Block called when the operation completes."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Receives nil on success, or an NSError on failure."}]}],"name":"completion"}],"kind":"parameters"},{"content":[{"anchor":"discussion","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Atomically associates a user ID with multiple email addresses and provides"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"confirmation when the operation completes. This is the recommended method","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"for user identification during authentication flows."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"Example","text":"Example"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Handle OAuth login with full user setup:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class OAuthLoginHandler {","","    func handleOAuthCallback(_ authResult: OAuthResult,","                            completion: @escaping (Result<Void, Error>) -> Void) {","","        \/\/ Extract user info from OAuth result","        let userId = authResult.userId","        var emails: [String] = []","","        if let primaryEmail = authResult.email {","            emails.append(primaryEmail)","        }","        if let verifiedEmails = authResult.verifiedEmails {","            emails.append(contentsOf: verifiedEmails.filter { $0 != authResult.email })","        }","","        \/\/ Set user and emails with confirmation","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUser(userId, emails: emails) { error in","            if let error = error {","                Logger.error(\"User setup failed: \\(error.localizedDescription)\")","                completion(.failure(error))","                return","            }","","            \/\/ User is now fully identified - set profile tags","            Pushwoosh.configure.setTags([","                \"oauth_provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"has_profile_picture\": authResult.profilePictureURL != nil,","                \"locale\": authResult.locale ?? Locale.current.identifier,","                \"first_login\": !self.hasExistingSession(for: userId)","            ])","","            Analytics.track(\"oauth_login_complete\", properties: [","                \"provider\": authResult.provider.rawValue,","                \"email_count\": emails.count","            ])","","            completion(.success(()))","        }","    }","}"]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setUser:emails:completion:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets user identifier and emails with completion handler."}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"minor":3,"major":0},"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"title":"setUser:emails:completion:","modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setUser:emails:completion:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setUser:emails:completion:","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Type Method"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"title":"PushwooshCore","kind":"symbol","role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","title":"PWConfiguration","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setUser:emails:completion:":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCor